                            <h4>Harmony and History: The Traditional Public Baths of Taza.</h4>
                        </div>
                        <p>The hammams, also known as traditional public baths, hold a special place in the daily life and culture of Taza, a city in northern Morocco. These hammams have a long history and are iconic places where locals gather to relax, cleanse, and socialize..</p>
                        <div class="destination-details-image">
