                            Hamam Boughlala is a famous and large popular hammam located in Taza, Morocco. It is an iconic venue cherished by the locals of the region as well as visitors seeking an authentic experience of the Moroccan hammam.

                            Hamam Boughlala stands out for its traditional ambiance and characteristic architecture. Inside, the walls are beautifully adorned with zellige tiles, Moroccan mosaics, and the floors are made of marble, creating a warm and soothing atmosphere as soon as you step through its doors.

                            This hammam offers a complete experience of the Moroccan hammam, with various services and treatments for the guests.
                        </p>

